# Required for the "Ask my AI Twin" chatbot in the Contact section.
# It calls Groq's free API through a Vercel serverless function
# (api/chat.js) so the key never reaches the browser.
#
# 1. Sign up free at https://console.groq.com
# 2. Create an API key
# 3. Copy this file to ".env" (for local `vercel dev`) and paste it below
#    — OR set it directly in Vercel: Project Settings -> Environment Variables
#
# Without this, the chatbot will show a friendly error and visitors can
# still reach you via the "Prefer email?" link.

GROQ_API_KEY=
